flowchart TD
  A[Open profile document vault] --> B{Choose source}
  B -->|Camera| C{Camera allowed?}
  B -->|File or photo| D[Validate MIME and size]
  C -->|No| E[Show settings and file fallback]
  C -->|Yes| D
  D -->|Unsupported or over 20 MB| F[Reject with recoverable message]
